In this article, Im going to cover a robust backend development use some best practices. The topics we are gonna cover will include
- CRUD and HTTP protocol
- Testing (with Jest because its popular)
- Database (we will do CRUD operation with filesytem so as not to introduce another learning curve)
- Containerization
- Microservices
- Deployment
- Dependency injection
- CI/CD
- Documentation (using Swagger)
- Authorization and Authentication
- Versioning and custom middleware
- Folder structuring